    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-agent knowledge presentation configuration. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Required on <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client_1a464c56ea8abd85c1f3b97a9558b9382a" kindref="member">Tryll::TryllClient::CreateAgent</ref> when the graph contains any <computeroutput>Retrieve</computeroutput> node; the server rejects the request otherwise. <computeroutput>messageTemplate</computeroutput> must contain <computeroutput>{knowledge}</computeroutput> and may contain <computeroutput>{user_message}</computeroutput> (only meaningful for <computeroutput>placement</computeroutput> == <computeroutput>InPlaceOfUser</computeroutput>). Unknown template tokens are a validation error returned as <computeroutput>ErrorResponse</computeroutput>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
